tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT userExperienceScore, sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf") group by userExperienceScore order by sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) desc

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT userExperienceScore, sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and not (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf") group by userExperienceScore order by sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) desc

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT userExperienceScore, count(userSessionId) FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf") group by userExperienceScore order by count(userSessionId) desc

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT userExperienceScore, count(userSessionId) FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and not (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf") group by userExperienceScore order by count(userSessionId) desc

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(userSessionId) as "Sessions" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /")

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) as "Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf")

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) as "Risk Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf") and (userExperienceScore ="TOLERATED" or userExperienceScore ="FRUSTRATED" or userExperienceScore ="UNDEFINED")

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) as "Lost Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and not (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf")

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) as "New User Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf") and newUser IS true

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select sum(usersession.doubleProperties.revenue) as "Returning User Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf") and newUser IS false

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select avg(useraction.duration) as "Duration" from usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /")

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT count(userSessionId) as "Conversions" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf")

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: SELECT count(userSessionId) as "Abandons" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and not (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf")

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select sum(useraction.errorCount) as "Errors" from usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /")

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select sum(numberOfRageClicks) as "Rage Clicks" FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /")

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Nonengaged Sessions" from usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"  and (useraction.name="loading of page /") and duration > 180000 and userActionCount < 10 and (useraction.name="loading of page /")

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT FUNNEL((useraction.name="loading of page /") AS "Home", (useraction.name="click on login") AS "Login", (useraction.name="click on search") AS "Search", (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-review.jsf") AS "Review", (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-payment.jsf") AS "Payment", (useraction.name="loading of page /orange-booking-finish.jsf") AS "Finish") FROM usersession where useraction.application="EasyTravel"
